{"id": 1971, "genre": 1001, "title": "你保持着哪一种特立独行？", "description": "如何不矫情地在这个社会保持自我？力求不一样还是守住内心原则，你觉得呢？", "record_count": 8898, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171023145522cdYfKLaXeTOrzsxA.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-26T03:00:45Z", "options": [{"id": 244224, "content": "人多的大众喜欢的热闹的都不去不关注不转发", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147220}, {"id": 244480, "content": "点赞多的 就不特立独行了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869548}, {"id": 244481, "content": "嘴上说不找女朋友，心里确非常想找一个。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1168415}, {"id": 244226, "content": "在学校的时候坚持六点起床，大二", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1167999}, {"id": 244482, "content": "做一个心地善良的好姑娘", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1139998}, {"id": 244994, "content": "未入社会 一身孤胆", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1169303}, {"id": 244483, "content": "确定自己的每一个决定都是遵从自己的内心", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1168420}, {"id": 254723, "content": "不穿爆款", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215280}, {"id": 244228, "content": "坚持在吃饭的时候按顺序吃完一种菜再吃另一种菜。哈哈！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1168008}, {"id": 244484, "content": "不被制度化", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752943}, {"id": 245508, "content": "只对吃和狗狗感兴趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1172499}, {"id": 244229, "content": "写代码最后必空一行", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1149266}, {"id": 244485, "content": "坚持只做喜欢的事！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797868}, {"id": 244230, "content": "坚持不以最大的恶意去揣摩别人的心思，坚持