: 1083186}, {"id": 245003, "content": "一个人大大方方走进男装店挑衣服并试穿。-并没有刻意排斥女装，只是我看中的服装风格正好出现在男装上而已。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461690}, {"id": 244236, "content": "真诚", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 514622}, {"id": 244492, "content": "坚持良知和道德原则，不因为大众的随波逐流造成的不正确的常态而接受这种常态，比如补课，比如浪费，比如为利益而放弃应有的公平之类！", "image": "img/option/option/20171026200753i8qkexazpDhTSvNK", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1168429}, {"id": 244237, "content": "坚持善良，保持好奇心，喜欢一切阳光美好的事物", "image": "img/option/option/20171026121603pNH9n1Oo7ct8EzyD", "praise_count": 76, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1167529}, {"id": 244493, "content": "上大学不化妆", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1168426}, {"id": 244238, "content": "不闲逛", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978470}, {"id": 244494, "content": "看电影只看豆瓣评分高的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1168434}, {"id": 244495, "content": "不抽烟", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1168434}, {"id": 245007, "content": "卸载微博很久", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1169880}, {"id": 246287, "content": "内心强大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174850}, {"id": 244240, "content": "不为了独特而独特 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 225, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 71166}, {"id": 245008, "content": "不玩lol不玩王者荣耀不玩吃鸡不玩魔兽不玩屁股。\n放假一定要写完作业才玩。\n在小卖部从来不挥霍。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915593}, {"id": 244241, "content": "不看宫廷剧…", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935711}, {"id": 244497, "content": "很色，喜欢大屁股", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 325289}, {"id": 244753, "content": "坚持看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "autho